<plot>Two old friends come together to cope with the death of one friend's wife. When coping turns to alcohol, however, a drunken decision unearths feelings in one of the men that exceeds mere friendship. That evening, he is presented with a difficult choice: to follow the path of his desires or to pretend he wished a close moment never happened. Which choice will he make, and in the morning, how will his friend react?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?261837</url></doc>
